adamiano001 01-14-26 08:31:47: From Tony Hoang: Hi Anthony,
Thank you for your patience. This device has been on-site and non-operational for several months, and with that,  I have instructed the IT team to gather the necessary information to get it fully functional.
The wireless MAC address for the AuditPro device is: 0c:23:69:55:f3:a2.
