in - Alyanna is on PTO and will test when she gets back. ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 7/1/2024 12:16:40 PM: Network team to change VLAN 243 to ST network. Alex Yuan working on configuration and will email Dean Demir and John Patty when he's done so John can add the firewall rules. ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 7/1/2024 11:50:19 AM: John Patty took firewall task. Told me VLAN 243 at this location is trusted, not semi-trusted as stated in BlueCat. Asked site to test. ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 6/26/2024 9:21:27 AM: Asked Alex Vazquez for update. ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 6/19/2024 10:45:58 AM: Firewall - SCTASK6351709 - Alex Vazquez ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 6/14/2024 9:56:38 AM: Modality onboarding: REQ4548805 ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 6/7/2024 8:41:18 AM: Email out to Marcus Warren asking for more information on connetivity of this device. ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 6/7/2024 8:37:01 AM: Meditech connectivity going through DOG IDEA/DEMAND process for Meditech connectivity. This effort is for getting the device connected to Meditech. ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 6/4/2024 7:16:23 AM: Response from Dhaval: Hello Anthony This site is not on Cerner I believe so we need some more information about it. We currently don't have any Cerner iBus interface for this site. Please let me know if you have any questions. ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 6/4/2024 7:15:16 AM: Hello Gary - Your MDICI request has been received and assigned the following project number: ID 2246 MTMC Sysmex XN Series Below are the connections requested for the device that I need clarification on: What system(s) will this device be connected to? Unknown Will Instrument Connect Through Middleware: (i.e. Telcor or RALS - please specify) Unknown If the device requires integration with an application/workstation/device select 2 of the following: New system workstation/device, Needs to be added to the network Working on a few of these Sysmex installs recently I would assume that we need to get an IP assigned and firewall rules in place to allow connectivity for remote support. I've added a few people to this thread that can hopefully let me know if this will also connect to a term server and then to Cerner. Here is how I imagine the device will need to connect: > If this looks correct I will need the MAC address of the XN unit. If this is also connecting through a term server to Cerner I would like that information to have the Design Engineer document on their technical design. Once I have all of that information I will assign resources and a start date. From the start date of the project it can take up to four weeks before the device is ready to test. Once this project is ready to test I will send out networking information with the technical design in a separate email. Let me know if you have any questions. ___________________________________________________________",2024-07-01,2024-06-14,2024-10-04,Northern California,660.0,2024-06-28,Completed,,21.0,4.0,116.0,2026-04-01 21:30:08.188085,CORLCYB001
