Mike Shelton,1679,,Southern California,GMHHC,Complete,Lab-MDI,2023-02-20,ID 1679 GMHHC Abbott ID Now,1,Testing complete per Dhaval.,Dhaval Pathak / Ramy Moawad / Kevin Deitch,"Anthony Damiano , 6/9/2023 8:45:48 AM: Testing complete per Dhaval. ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 6/2/2023 8:32:57 AM: Unit to go-live next week. ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 6/1/2023 3:07:47 PM: Per Dhaval - we have a connection now, facility to go live next week with this interface. ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 5/31/2023 10:11:09 AM: SCTASK4357082 for Archie's review. ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 5/26/2023 8:36:13 AM: To go live on 5/30/23. ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 5/19/2023 8:08:37 AM: Waiting on moratorium, tentative go-live last week of May. ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 5/12/2023 8:41:49 AM: Waiting on Kevin to finish validation before assigning a go-live date. ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 4/25/2023 3:02:36 PM: From Ramy: We have successfully tested the instrument for connectivity and the interface appears to be ready for sample testing. ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 4/21/2023 8:39:14 AM: Kevin working on validation. ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 4/14/2023 8:44:37 AM: Kevin is working on validation. ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 3/31/2023 9:02:08 AM: Dhaval meeting with Kevin to go over connectivity testing. ___________________________________________________________ Anthony Damiano , 3/20/2023 2:31:10 PM: Kevin Deitch working with Dhaval for testing on this unit. ____________________________________________