Lenczewski, Michael - PHX , 7/9/2020 8:13:34 AM:
Will the analyzer be directly connected with a cable to the Cisco Security Appliance? Yes, the Cisco Appliance is considered a component of the Echo Lumena.Will the Cisco Security Appliance installed by Vendor inside the analyzer? No, we install the device near or around the analyzer depending on available space.If inside the analyzer, how 2 analyzers will use single appliance in CRMC? Not applicable
Will the Cisco Security Appliance installed by Vendor outside the analyzer? YesWhere will it be installed then? Near or around the analyzer depending on available space.
Will it be physically secured in enclosure to prevent access? At the discretion of the facility, Immucor does not provide an enclosure.
Will the analyzer be directly connected via network to the Cisco Security Appliance? We NAT the analyzers behind the cisco device in a 192.168.1.x network, the cisco then speaks on behalf of the analyzer(s) into the network.
